      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence, round-off, and solver tolerance effects quantified and shown to be negligible relative to discretization error.",
      "rationale": "Residual convergence plots provided but no formal analysis of solver tolerance contribution to QoI error. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5; not assessed."
    },
