      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent re-analysis or formal review of simulation setup, boundary condition application, and post-processing scripts by a qualified analyst not involved in original simulation.",
      "rationale": "No independent re-analysis performed. Single analyst team conducted all simulations and post-processing. Use error contribution cannot be bounded. Flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
    {
