      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model form uncertainty through comparison of multiple model variants against experimental data.",
      "rationale": "Single turbulence model (SST k-omega) and single hemolysis model (Giersiepen power-law) used without alternative model comparison. Model form uncertainty is the dominant unquantified source of error. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
